prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card front cover, in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds.

The scene features cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan, highly resembling the people in the reference photo. Lao Lao, on the left, is an East Asian woman with long dark brown hair and round, thin-framed glasses, wearing a light yellow halter top with a red floral pattern. Jordan, on the right, is a man with tan skin and short, spiky dark hair, wearing a plain white t-shirt. They are both smiling warmly.

The humorous and fantastical scene depicts them sitting inside a giant, steaming bowl of Chinese porridge (congee), using oversized boba tea straws to playfully slurp it up. Floating in the porridge around them like little islands are several plump, happy-looking soup dumplings (xiao long bao) with cartoon smiley faces. The steam rising from the porridge is soft and wispy, rendered in delicate watercolor washes. The background is a simple, light-colored watercolor wash to keep the focus on the couple and the food.

Centered in the middle of the card, below the main illustration, is the text "Happy Birthday to my Dumpling!" written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
